S H E F F Y   O B E R O I

latestIgtvVideos.title: Our love story ✨💛
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
He used to be a backbencher and I was the 'Frontline Girl' having our classes parallel to each other. Right from the first lecture to the very end of the day, our work was to stare and gaze in admiration. 
Hey Baby, 
I won't lie but I was the one who fell in love with you first! I wanted to shower all my love but you were lost somewhere chilling and drinking with your friends! 
From constant looks to endless fights to resentful nights, how 6 months of SACCM passed I still don't know.. And, just when i was about to give up, I got "The Proposal." I still remember that "SACCM Atrium" where you popped the question and I blushed and said "Yes", thus started the Journey of "Kaju and Suw."
Our beautiful love story saw its own bunch of ups and downs, and came 23rd July 2015 when you asked: "Will you marry me?" Thing's weren't easy, we had our rough patch of 1 year, broke up for months but like a fairytale: "We came back Stronger and Firmer!" My Love, today i wanna dedicate this video to "US and Our Unbreakable Love" and of course to SACCM who made " SUW said yes" made you "Mine Forever!" SACCM I love you for giving me suw ❤️
